oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sitka's Model Mile
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of "Sitka's Model Mile" as it was developed by Chapman, who owned the store in the background.
The area now has houses on both sides and a large Church of Christ.
